- jwt
  https://github.com/gbrlsnchs/jwt
  Use this instead of custom X-Auth-Token header.

- Learn about writing http middlewares in Go
  https://www.nicolasmerouze.com/middlewares-golang-best-practices-examples
  Specifically the panic recovery one.

- structured logging
  https://github.com/Sirupsen/logrus

- Go error contexts
  https://github.com/juju/errgo
  Or just read the errors package and see what's available there.